General.Name: Proteomics Intl Labs Ltd
General.Description: Proteomics International Laboratories Limited operates as a medical technology company with a focus on the area of proteomics. It provides PromarkerD, a predictive test for diabetic kidney disease; and develops diagnostic tests for endometriosis and giardia. The company also offers analytical services, including specialist contract research. The company was founded in 2001 and is based in Perth, Australia.
